title: Independent candidate Zulfiqar Ali wins NA-34 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate, Zulfiqar Ali has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-34, Nowshera-II by securing 95,692 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf Parliamentarian candidate, Imran Khattak who bagged 32,698 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 47.12%.
